Flub.Name: Map
Flub.Description: T

Flub.Name: Simplify
Flub.Description: Simplify the terrain contours. Use this when the terrain has a lot of small detail and the contours start looking too complex and chaotic.

Flub.Name: Smooth Land Gradient
Flub.Description: Smooth the land colors across contour levels.

Flub.Name: Smooth Water Gradient
Flub.Description: Smooth the water colors across contour levels.

Flub.Name: Land
Flub.Description: T

Flub.Name: Contours
Flub.Description: Number of contours for dividing the terrain. Secondary contours will be generated between these contours.

Flub.Name: Primary Contours
Flub.Description: Intensity of the primary contours. Use 0 to hide.

Flub.Name: Secondary Contours
Flub.Description: Intensity of the secondary contours. Use 0 to hide.

Flub.Name: Contour Color
Flub.Description: Color of the contour lines.

Flub.Name: Water
Flub.Description: T

Flub.Name: Process Water
Flub.Description: When enabled, the water gradient is processed. Otherwise water is left as a flat shape.

Flub.Name: Contours
Flub.Description: Number of contours for dividing the water. Secondary contours will be generated between these contours.

Flub.Name: Primary Contours
Flub.Description: Intensity of the primary contours in the water. Use 0 to hide.

Flub.Name: Secondary Contours
Flub.Description: Intensity of the secondary contours in the water. Use 0 to hide.

Flub.Name: Water Contour Color
Flub.Description: Color of the contour lines in the water.

Flub.Name: Grid
Flub.Description: T

Flub.Name: Grid Lines
Flub.Description: Number of grid lines on either axis. Further subdivisions would be created within those grid lines.

Flub.Name: Primary Grid Intensity
Flub.Description: Intensity of primary grid lines. Use 0 to hide.

Flub.Name: Secondary Grid Intensity
Flub.Description: Intensity of the secondary grid lines. Use 0 to hide.

Flub.Name: Grid Color
Flub.Description: Color of the grid lines.

Flub.Name: Pixels
Flub.Description: T

Flub.Name: Contour Pixel Size
Flub.Description: Size of contour lines in pixels.

Flub.Name: Boundary Pixel Size
Flub.Description: Size of the contour dividing water and land in pixels.

Flub.Name: Grid Pixel Size
Flub.Description: Size of the grid lines in pixels.
